### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@postId = 6927397f8e36cafb6a4f73ee
@userId = 692735878e36cafb6a4f73e3

### Crear un nuevo post
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{userId}}",
  "content": "Este es mi primer post en FitExpress!",
  "image": "https://example.com/image.jpg"
}

### Obtener todos los posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/posts/all

### Obtener posts de un usuario específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/posts/user/{{userId}}

### Obtener un post específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/posts/{{postId}}

### Actualizar un post
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/posts/{{postId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Contenido actualizado del post",
  "image": "https://example.com/new-image.jpg"
}

### Dar like a un post
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/posts/{{postId}}/like
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{userId}}"
}

### Quitar like de un post
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/posts/{{postId}}/like
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{userId}}"
}

### Agregar comentario a un post
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/posts/{{postId}}/comment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{userId}}",
  "text": "¡Excelente post!"
}

### Eliminar un post
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/posts/{{postId}}
